[To find Jharkhand on a map, go to: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jharkhand, and the location of Simdega can be seen at: http://www.fallingrain.com/world/IN/38/Simdega.html.

There are few reports of anthrax in Jharkhand. In 2010, there was a singular bovine event with some 300 cattle cases. Otherwise, it occurred in elephants in the Seraikela Forest Division in 2004 and 2005 and in Samba in 2013 in the Dalma Wildlife Sanctuary. - Mod.MHJ

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=3350673,306.]
